snippet.title: ***CANCELLED***MALIYAH VERGENZ AMBER ALERT 25SEP2012
snippet.description:
THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS DIVISION OF EMERGENCY MANAGEMENT. THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT NETWORK. THE GARLAND POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR MALIYAH VERGENZ...A HISPANIC FEMALE...2 YEARS OLD...DATE OF BIRTH IS MAY 5TH 2010...BROWN HAIR...BROWN EYES...AND UNKNOWN CLOTHING DESCRIPTION.
POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR PATRICIA GARCIA IN CONNECTION WITH THE ABDUCTION...OTHERWISE KNOWN AS PATRICIA BERUMAN...OTHERWISE KNOWN AS PATRICIA CHAVEZ...OTHERWISE KNOWN AS PATRICIA CRUCES...HISPANIC FEMALE...38 YEARS OLD...DATE OF BIRTH APRIL 23 1974. HEIGHT 5 FOOT 3 INCHES...250 LBS...BROWN HAIR...BROWN EYES...CURLY HAIR.THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A CHRYSLER...1998...ASPIRE WITH AN UNKNOWN PAPER LICENSE PLATE NUMBER. THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN GARLAND TEXAS.LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR IMMEDIATE DANGER.IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE GARLAND POLICE DEPARTMENT.
